    "5 Challenges and opportunities in AI implementation for food safety, quality and security /doi.org/10.1007/s42452-025-06472-w Review 4.4/doi.org/10.1007/s42452-025-06472-wWorkforce training and skill development Constraint: The adoption of new technologies often requires significant investment in workforce training and skill development.",
